<p>
<b><i>NewWave,</i> Version 4.0</b><br>
Hewlett-Packard Co., 974 E. Arques Ave., Sunnyvale, CA 94086; 408-720-3000.<br>
<b>List Price:</b> $195. <br>
<b>Requires:</b> 2.5MB RAM (4MB recommended), 6.8MB hard disk space, Windows 3.0 or later.<br>
<b>In Short:</b> <i>NewWave</i> takes object-oriented Windows to its logical extreme by 
replacing files and programs with objects and tools. Its automation tools are 
especially complete.
</p>

